Context: The College, George Brown College, is committed to reducing its ecological footprint by minimizing waste production and maximizing recyclability and reuse options. For application deadlines, college news, events, tours, and more updates, visitors can sign up on the website. Visitors can also connect with the college on its social media hub. The information on the website is subject to change without notice and should not be considered as a representation, offer or warranty. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
